<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Email Verification Code - MyQCM</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fc;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #ffffff;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4081, #ff79a7);
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: url('https://res.cloudinary.com/ddqioccgt/image/upload/v1740635000/myqcm_pattern.png');
      opacity: 0.1;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .header img {
      max-width: 140px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 35px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #ff4081;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .content p {
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .otp-box {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ffffff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4081, #ff79a7);
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: inline-block;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .verification-notice {
      background-color: #f9f5ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #ff4081;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      text-align: left;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .verification-notice p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #eee;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      padding: 20px 35px 30px;
      background-color: #f9fafc;
      border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
    }
    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #999;
    }
    .contact-info a {
      color: #ff4081;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        margin: 10px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 25px 20px;
      }
      .otp-box {
        font-size: 22px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgxaezwuv/image/upload/v1748615201/MyQCM_logo_zxe7yu_dysxal.png" alt="MyQCM Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Email Verification</h2>
      <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Use the 6-digit code below to verify your email address for your MyQCM account.</p>

      <div class="otp-box">
        <%= otp_code %>
      </div>

      <div class="verification-notice">
        <p>This code is valid for the next 10 minutes. Do not share it with anyone.</p>
      </div>

      <p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777; margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always here to help!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 MyQCM | All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="contact-info">
        <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@myqcmdz.com">support@myqcmdz.com</a></p>
        <p>You're receiving this email because you signed up for MyQCM.</p>
        <p><a href="{{privacyPolicyLink}}">Privacy Policy</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
